'''Kalbari al-Durrat al-Amwaj ibn Jari''' was a [[noble marid]] and the Great Padishah of the Marid in [[1367 DR]],{{AQ-time}} who ruled her subjects from her court in the [[Citadel of Ten Thousand Pearls]] on the [[Elemental Plane of Water]].
